---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Engineered Systems | Cain Anthony Macias">
  <header class="mb-12 mt-12">
    <a href="/" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors no-underline">&larr; Back to Profile</a>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-2">Engineered Systems</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400">Production-grade deployments and architectural case studies.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
    <article class="border border-zinc-800 p-8 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/50 hover:border-zinc-600 transition-colors">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 mt-0 border-none">Enterprise B2B Ordering Architecture</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6 text-base">Architected a full-stack Django platform on AWS featuring a dynamic tiered-pricing engine and strict Section 508 compliance.</p>
      <a href="/projects/b2b-ordering-platform/" class="text-white hover:text-zinc-300 no-underline font-medium">Read Case Study &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article class="border border-zinc-800 p-8 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/50 hover:border-zinc-600 transition-colors">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 mt-0 border-none">AutoQuotes-to-HubSpot Sync Engine</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6 text-base">Engineered a decoupled Python ETL pipeline and custom Ubuntu server to sanitize inventory data and autonomously sync with HubSpot CRM.</p>
      <a href="/projects/python-automation-engine/" class="text-white hover:text-zinc-300 no-underline font-medium">Read Case Study &rarr;</a>
    </article>

    <article class="border border-zinc-800 p-8 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900/50 hover:border-zinc-600 transition-colors">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 mt-0 border-none">Epicor Eclipse Migration & Audit</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6 text-base">Executed a zero-downtime transition of 500,000+ records from Epicor Eclipse to HubSpot using a custom Python Audit Server.</p>
      <a href="/projects/enterprise-migration/" class="text-white hover:text-zinc-300 no-underline font-medium">Read Case Study &rarr;</a>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>